<PageLayout title={`${title} | Better Lives Building Tribes`} schema={schema} description="Your heart races. Your chest feels tight. You get dizzy or nauseous for no clear reason. You have been to multiple doctors. They run tests. Everything comes back normal. They tell you it is anxiety, b">
